# Read `agent.md` First

- Before making edits, proposing architecture changes, or running substantive implementation work, read `agent.md` in the repository root.
- Follow guidance in `agent.md` for workflow, script style, and approval boundaries.
- If instructions in chat conflict with `agent.md`, ask for clarification before proceeding.
- Avoid adding new guideline documents if the same guidance already exists in `agent.md`.
